            "title": "滬指開市升10點 深成指升42點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段造好，上證綜指以4150點開市，升10點或0.25%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14371點，亦升42點或0.29%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數升19點或0.42%，開報4725點；創業板指數開市報3359點，升17點或0.51%。</p>\n</div>",
