            "title": "深鐵向萬科提供23.6億股東貸款",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">萬科企業(02202)公布，第一大股東深圳市地鐵集團向公司提供不超過23.6億元(人民幣‧下同)股東借款。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">借款主要用於償還公司在公開市場發行的債券本金與利息。借款期限：36個月，借款利率：定價基準為每筆借款提款日前一工作日全國銀行間同業拆借中心公布的1年期貸款市場報價利率（LPR），浮動點數為減66個基點，目前為2.34%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15618090-%e6%b7%b1%e9%90%b5%e5%90%91%e8%90%ac%e7%a7%91%e6%8f%90%e4%be%9b23-6%e5%84%84%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e8%b2%b8%e6%ac%be",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02202.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 09:24:14",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "曹操出行折讓約9%配股籌3.9億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">曹操出行(02643)公布，擬配股集資近3.9億元；配股價32.46元，較該股昨收市價35.66元折讓約8.97%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：曹操出行官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_FI_source-web_CaoCao-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：曹操出行官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250430_FI_source-web_CaoCao-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：曹操出行官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價35.27元計，配股價較之折讓約7.97%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資淨額約3.83億元，其中約67.7%用於發展國內外Robotaxi業務；約22.3%用於擴張公司企業服務；約10%用於營運資金及其他一般企業用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15618064-%e6%9b%b9%e6%93%8d%e5%87%ba%e8%a1%8c%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%93%e7%b4%849%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c3-9%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241031_FI_source-web_CaoCao-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-28 09:19:03",
